    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD model satisfies the stated requirement that hemolysis predictions be sufficiently accurate and not cause meaningful concern for patient safety. All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2, and the 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 expectations. The relative hemolysis index predictions agree with experimental data within acceptable bounds across all five operating points, and the model is judged adequate for the intended use in the COU.",
